FIG. 2 is a schematic representation of the lighting system of the present invention illustrating the major components thereof;


FIG. 3 is a schematic representation of a portion of the lighting system of the present invention illustrating beam divergence in one mode of operation of the present invention;


FIG. 4 is a schematic representation of a portion of the lighting system of the present invention illustrating beam divergence in another mode of the present invention;


FIG. 5 is a schematic representation of a portion of the present invention illustrating an embodiment of this invention utilizing a unique reflective/divergence controlling element in one mode of operation;


