FIG. 8 is a front view illustrating the beam distribution means and incorporating the mechanism utilized for movement thereof;


FIG. 9 is a side view of the beam distributing means illustrating both the mechanism for movement of the distributing means as well as its interconnection to a beam-conveying mechanism;


