FIG. 10B is a schematic representation of the lighting system of this invention illustrating a beam-conveying mechanism of another configuration;


FIGS. 11A and 11B are pictorial, schematic representations of another embodiment of the present invention illustrating the utilization of reflective leaves within the beam-conveying mechanism;


FIG. 12 is a plan view of a ceiling illustrating various configurations of the lighting system of the present invention incorporated therein.
